data.description: What you've been searching to find at new improved price! Welcome to this lovely 4 bedroom home steps away from the Ross Barnett Reservoir.  You will love the spacious feel of this comfortable home where everyone can have their own space, including the bonus of an enclosed sunroom which is not part of the square footage total.  The bright crisp quartz countertops in the kitchen along with its brick look ceramic tile backsplash is a wonderful backdrop for all those who love to cook and entertain there.  There are 2 ½ baths and separate laundry room convenient to the work areas in the house.  The 4 bedrooms are split with the primary bedroom offering a calming retreat.  If you love being outdoors, grab a cold refreshment and enjoy the large deck overlooking a lush backyard.  You can also live like you're on vacation since you are steps away from the water with its thousands of acres for water activities, public parks, disc golf course, walking and biking trails.   This home is on a cul-de-sac and minutes away from shopping, restaurants and all the best Rankin County has to offer.  Come see it and make it your own!
